'''非洲刺毛鼠屬'''（學名：{{lang|la|''Acomys''}}），[[哺乳綱|哺乳綱]]、[[囓齒目|囓齒目]]、[[鼠科|鼠科]]一[[属|属]]的[[物种|物种]]，[[非洲攀鼠亞科|非洲攀鼠亞科]]四個屬之一<ref name = MSW3>{{MSW3 Muroidea | id = 13000997 | pages = 1194–1201 | heading = Genus ''Acomys''}}</ref>。外形上與[[小鼠属|小鼠属]]（''Mus''）物種相似，非洲刺毛鼠屬物種的體型細小，有無毛的[[鳞|鳞]][[尾|尾]]，不過遺傳學證據表明本屬物種與[[沙鼠|沙鼠]]的關係更為密切<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Steppan | first1 = S. | last2 = Adkins | first2 = R. | last3 = Anderson | first3 = J. | doi = 10.1080/10635150490468701 | title = Phylogeny and Divergence-Date Estimates of Rapid Radiations in Muroid Rodents Based on Multiple Nuclear Genes | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_systematic-biology_2004-08_53_4/page/533 | journal = Systematic Biology | volume = 53 | issue = 4 | pages = 533–553 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15371245| pmc = }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chevret |first1=P. |first2=C. |last2=Denys |first3=J.-J. |last3=Jaeger |first4=J |last4=Michaux |first5=F. M. |last5=Catzeflis |year=1993 |title=Molecular evidence that the spiny mouse (''Acomys'') is more closely related to [[沙鼠|gerbils]] (Gerbillinae) than to the true mice (Murinae) |journal=''[[Proceedings_of_the_National_Academy_of_Sciences|Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences]]'' |location=USA |volume=90 |pages=3433-3436 |language=en }}</ref>。

==下属物种==
本屬包括以下各物種：
*{{tsl|en|Western Saharan spiny mouse||Western Saharan spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys airensis''
*[[开罗刺鼠|开罗刺鼠]] ''[[Acomys_cahirinus|Acomys cahirinus]]''
*{{tsl|en|Chudeau's spiny mouse||Chudeau's spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys chudeaui''
*{{tsl|en|Asia Minor spiny mouse||Asia Minor spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys cilicicus''
*{{tsl|en|Gray spiny mouse||Gray spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys cineraceus''
*{{tsl|en|Eastern spiny mouse|東方刺毛鼠}} ''[[Acomys_dimidiatus|Acomys dimidiatus]]''
*{{tsl|en|Fiery spiny mouse||Fiery spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys ignitus''
*{{tsl|en|Johan's spiny mouse||Johan's spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys johannis''
*{{tsl|en|Kemp's spiny mouse||Kemp's spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys kempi''
*{{tsl|en|Louise's spiny mouse||Louise's spiny mouse}}, '' Acomys louisae''
*{{tsl|en|Crete spiny mouse|小非洲刺毛鼠}} ''[[Acomys_minous|Acomys minous]]''
*{{tsl|en|Mullah spiny mouse||Mullah spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys mullah''
*''[[Acomys_muzei|Acomys muzei]]''
*{{tsl|en|Cyprus spiny mouse||Cyprus spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys nesiotes''
*''[[Acomys_ngurui|Acomys ngurui]]''
*{{tsl|en|Percival's spiny mouse||Percival's spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys percivali''
*[[金刺鼠|金刺鼠]] ''[[Acomys_russatus|Acomys russatus]]''
*{{tsl|en|Seurat's spiny mouse||Seurat's spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys seurati''
*{{tsl|en|Southern African spiny mouse||Southern African spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys spinosissimus''
*{{tsl|en|Cape spiny mouse||Cape spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys subspinosus''
*{{tsl|en|Wilson's spiny mouse||Wilson's spiny mouse}}, ''Acomys wilsoni''

